thread.title: BRIEF-New Jersey Resources Q1 Earnings Per Share $1.42

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-New Jersey Resources Q1 Earnings Per Share $1.42
text:
Feb 8 (Reuters) - New Jersey Resources Corp:
* NEW JERSEY RESOURCES REPORTS FIRST-QUARTER FISCAL 2018 RESULTS AND RAISES EARNINGS GUIDANCE FOR THE YEAR
* Q1 EARNINGS PER SHARE $1.42 * ‍NJR RAISED ITS FISCAL 2018 NFE GUIDANCE TO $2.55 TO $2.65 FROM $1.75 TO $1.85 PER SHARE​
* SEES ‍LONG-TERM ANNUAL NFE PER SHARE GROWTH RATE RANGE ADJUSTED TO 6 TO 8 PERCENT​
* QTRLY ‍TOTAL OPERATING REVENUES $705.3 MILLION VERSUS $541.0 MILLION​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
